		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My CopyCart can do this, if you have your dev cart wired up just right.  It has a 72 pin nes connector on one side (to put your devcart into) and a usb connector on the other.  It's still a prototype though, I haven't made more than one of them yet.

		

